Look at me.

31:50.240 --> 31:51.662
Look at Emily.

31:53.440 --> 31:54.930
- Sally, what's going on?

31:54.980 --> 31:56.129
- I know, I know, I know.

31:56.180 --> 31:58.239
Look, you need to
go find Josh right now.

31:58.280 --> 31:59.577
I'm gonna go
find Aidan, OK?

31:59.610 --> 32:01.419
- (Crying): What's
happening to me?

32:01.450 --> 32:03.111
