32:04.350 --> 32:05.511
- OK.

32:05.550 --> 32:06.711
- Go.

32:06.750 --> 32:08.479
(Grunting)

32:08.520 --> 32:10.579
Aidan, stop!

32:10.620 --> 32:12.987
- Don't listen to her.
She's scared.

32:13.030 --> 32:15.397
It's only natural.
She'll get over it.

32:15.430 --> 32:18.730
- This is all for you.
We have a chance now.

32:18.770 --> 32:21.364
- Whatever it is
you think that you heard,

32:21.400 --> 32:24.006
whatever you're thinking,
it's all a lie.

32:24.040 --> 32:26.259
It's all a lie.

32:26.310 --> 32:29.075
I need you, OK? Please!

32:29.110 --> 32:30.475
Please?

32:30.510 --> 32:32.740
(Whispering):
Please don't leave me!

32:32.780 --> 32:35.317
Please don't leave me!

32:42.690 --> 32:44.579
(Sally sighing)

32:51.070 --> 32:54.392
- All right, what the hell
is happening to me?

32:57.500 --> 32:59.207
(Sighing)

33:02.040 --> 33:04.407
(Breathing unevenly)

33:08.550 --> 33:10.416
- (Sobbing): Oh no!

33:11.650 --> 33:15.154
NO, NO, NO, NO!

33:17.690 --> 33:20.751
(Sobbing):
No, no, no...

33:22.760 --> 33:25.320
Oh God! Oh God!

33:25.370 --> 33:27.190
Oh, Nora!

33:32.670 --> 33:34.729
(Whispering): Oh God!

33:34.780 --> 33:36.202
She was right.

33:36.240 --> 33:38.641
All this death,

33:38.680 --> 33:40.444
it was always me.

