33:57.560 --> 34:01.690
I love you. I love you!

34:01.740 --> 34:03.538
- (Nora): Josh?

34:03.570 --> 34:06.164
Josh, what are you doing?
Stop it!

34:06.210 --> 34:08.268
What's going on?
- No! No! Oh my God!

34:08.310 --> 34:10.699
- Stop! Put the knife down.
- I'm so sorry!

34:10.739 --> 34:14.119
- Don't be sorry! Whatever you
