34:14.150 --> 34:15.275
- It's all my fault!

34:15.320 --> 34:16.446
- Put down the knife!

34:16.480 --> 34:18.244
Please look at me!
Look at me!

34:18.290 --> 34:19.746
I'm here!
I'm here!

34:19.790 --> 34:21.382
I'm here! Please!

34:23.460 --> 34:25.428
Please!
It's gonna be OK.

34:25.460 --> 34:27.656
I'm here.
We're gonna be OK.

34:27.690 --> 34:30.523
Just put down
the knife, please.

34:30.560 --> 34:31.789
- You're not a ghost!

34:31.830 --> 34:34.629
- All of us
are gonna be OK.

34:34.670 --> 34:36.138
(Sobbing)

34:36.170 --> 34:37.331
- Josh!

34:37.370 --> 34:38.337
- You OK?

34:38.370 --> 34:39.565
- We gotta go.

34:39.610 --> 34:41.271
- Let's go!

34:41.310 --> 34:44.768
OK, T'll explain that later.
We need to get out of here now!

34:44.810 --> 34:46.277
Come on, everybody.

34:46.310 --> 34:47.744
Aidan, come on!

34:47.780 --> 34:50.545
- (Aidan): Wait!
Just hold on for a second!

34:52.219 --> 34:54.210
(All panting)

34:54.260 --> 34:55.409
- (Nora):
Oh my God!

34:55.460 --> 34:56.859
- Oh, zero improvement!

34:56.889 --> 34:59.484
- What is going on?
- Do you see what's happening?

34:59.530 --> 35:01.851
Every door we go through
leads to the wrong room.

35:01.900 --> 35:03.425
This wall is
now sealed up

35:03.460 --> 35:06.464
after a giant,
sledgehammered hole was in it

35:06.500 --> 35:07.467
10 minutes ago.

35:07.500 --> 35:08.763
It's the house!

35:08.800 --> 35:10.859
- What the hell are
you saying? What?

35:10.900 --> 35:13.608
- Why don't you shut up
and let her explain, Aidan?

35:14.840 --> 35:18.470
- Guys, Ramona's
not a ghost.

35:20.210 --> 35:22.850
She's the evil of
this house, personified,

35:22.880 --> 35:25.781
and she's not
letting us out alive.

35:25.820 --> 35:28.380
- That's the
condensed version,

35:28.420 --> 35:30.354
but I can tell
you all get the gist.

35:30.390 --> 35:32.529
- You know what, Ramona?
You lose, though,

35:32.560 --> 35:34.324
because nobody here
offed themselves,

35:34.360 --> 35:35.521
nobody killed each other.

35:35.560 --> 35:37.358
Our bond is
stronger than you.

35:37.400 --> 35:40.597
So I guess you didn't really
think about that, did you?

35:40.630 --> 35:42.359
- I have time.

35:45.940 --> 35:50.207
Look at that.
Soon enough, I'll have help.

35:50.240 --> 35:51.901
- Aidan?

35:54.350 --> 35:55.442
Aidan, it's me!

35:55.480 --> 35:56.948
- How the hell
did he get in here?

35:56.980 --> 35:58.379
- Open that wall.

35:58.420 --> 35:59.910
You open that wall
right now!

35:59.950 --> 36:01.759
(Wall crackling)

36:01.790 --> 36:03.189
- Wait!

36:03.220 --> 36:05.450
(Scoffing)

36:05.490 --> 36:06.753
Aidan, wait. Don't!

36:06.790 --> 36:09.350
- (Josh):
Hey! No!

36:09.400 --> 36:11.220
No!

36:11.270 --> 36:13.261
(Josh grunting)

36:13.300 --> 36:14.961
- Hey, pal! I said
I'd help you out,

36:15.000 --> 36:17.367
but now is not
exactly the best time.

36:17.400 --> 36:20.506
- Stop it. I'm gonna give you
one last chance.

36:20.540 --> 36:22.201
Tell me the truth.

36:22.240 --> 36:23.799
- The truth?

36:23.840 --> 36:25.945
Buddy, I don't
want any secrets.

36:25.980 --> 36:27.948
- Stop lying!

36:29.320 --> 36:30.810
I know Josh killed her,

36:30.850 --> 36:33.342
so stop lying to me for once.

36:33.390 --> 36:36.212
- OK, Kenny, please,
just listen to me for a second.

36:36.260 --> 36:39.525
- What? What could you possibly
say to me right now, huh?

36:39.560 --> 36:40.857
I have been
listening to you.

36:40.890 --> 36:42.551
I followed you,
and I trusted you

36:42.600 --> 36:45.968
and you told me that there was
a special bond between us.

36:46.000 --> 36:47.593
You remember that?

36:47.630 --> 36:49.337
- Yeah, and I meant that.

36:49.370 --> 36:51.805
What happened to Astrid,
I'm heartbroken. I really am.

36:51.840 --> 36:54.502
And I wanted to tell you,
but I was scared.

36:54.540 --> 36:56.599
I was scared of
how you would react.

36:56.640 --> 36:58.301
I was scared of this.

36:58.350 --> 37:00.478
I was scared that
it would come between us.

37:00.510 --> 37:02.319
- Josh is what's between us,

37:02.350 --> 37:04.489
and you choose him
again and again.

37:04.520 --> 37:06.340
- I would never
choose Josh.

37:06.390 --> 37:07.539
Look, what Josh did...

37:07.590 --> 37:08.557
(Sighing)

37:08.590 --> 37:09.853
...that's not who he is.

37:09.890 --> 37:12.621
He regrets it, and he's
gonna carry that guilt

37:12.660 --> 37:14.025
for the rest of his life.

37:14.060 --> 37:16.757
- I don't care. That's not
good enough for Astrid.

37:16.800 --> 37:19.269
- Maybe not.

37:20.600 --> 37:24.707
But what good is gonna
come of this, huh?

37:24.740 --> 37:28.904
Look, I already told you
that revenge is--

37:28.940 --> 37:30.931
- Is what she deserves.
I know.

37:32.380 --> 37:34.474
I loved her.

37:34.520 --> 37:38.548
And unlike you, I honour
the people that I love.

37:44.960 --> 37:47.452
But first I have to kill you,

37:47.490 --> 37:51.996
so I don't have to hear another
lie come out of your mouth.

37:52.030 --> 37:53.520
- You don't wanna do that.

37:53.570 --> 37:55.459
And this is gonna sound crazy,

37:55.500 --> 37:58.504
but I gotta get you out
of this house right now!

37:58.540 --> 38:00.360
- We have to do something.

38:00.410 --> 38:02.799
You should be able
to get out of here, right?

38:02.840 --> 38:05.343
- I can't!
Her control is beyond me.

38:05.380 --> 38:06.541
I can't get in or out.

38:06.580 --> 38:08.639
Why would you do this?

38:08.680 --> 38:12.014
Why would you let Kenny in?
What purpose does he serve?

38:12.050 --> 38:14.849
- You killed Bishop,
got your vengeance.

38:14.890 --> 38:16.051
(Sighing)

38:16.090 --> 38:17.683
Now's my turn.

38:17.720 --> 38:21.395
Circle of life
or something, huh?

38:22.630 --> 38:24.325
- It's happening,

38:24.370 --> 38:26.395
just as it was meant to.

38:26.430 --> 38:30.389
One by one,
you will all fall.

38:30.440 --> 38:32.807
- Aidan!
- Baby, hold on!

38:34.140 --> 38:37.007
- Wait a sec.
Did you call her "baby"?

38:37.040 --> 38:39.805
Ah, we have
something in common.

38:39.850 --> 38:41.818
We both love
dead girls.

38:41.850 --> 38:43.079
- Hold on, hold on!

38:43.120 --> 38:45.088
(Both grunting)

38:45.120 --> 38:46.417
(Aidan groaning)

38:55.560 --> 38:58.325
(Both grunting)

39:00.870 --> 39:04.761
- Admit it! Admit that you were
never a true father to me!

39:04.810 --> 39:06.835
(Groaning)

39:09.710 --> 39:10.905
Admit it!

39:10.940 --> 39:12.044
(Both grunting)

39:16.550 --> 39:18.040
(Aidan groaning)

39:19.950 --> 39:23.079
Don't you see?
This is why I did this!

39:23.120 --> 39:24.656
I did this for you!

39:24.690 --> 39:26.852
I rebuilt this town for you.

39:29.760 --> 39:32.661
(Both grunting)

39:46.610 --> 39:48.544
- (Whispering):
Oh my God!

39:48.580 --> 39:50.674
Hey, no, no, no!
Don't move, don't move!

39:50.720 --> 39:52.085
Look at me, look at me.

39:52.120 --> 39:53.884
Just stay calm.
All right?

39:53.920 --> 39:55.456
(Exhaling sharply)

39:55.490 --> 39:56.685
Um...

39:56.720 --> 39:58.154
- (Whispering):
Oh, this is it.

39:58.190 --> 39:59.487
- No, no, no.

39:59.530 --> 40:02.556
Everything's OK.
Everything's OK.

40:02.600 --> 40:05.160
- No, no.
This is OK.

40:05.200 --> 40:08.431
I was ready for this.
I have been.

40:08.470 --> 40:10.564
- No, no, no.
We're gonna fix this.

40:10.600 --> 40:11.704
Trust me! Trust me!

40:11.740 --> 40:13.105
- Shhh! It's OK.

40:13.140 --> 40:16.110
I mean, I got to live a lot
longer than I was meant to,

40:16.140 --> 40:18.848
and I got to be with
a beautiful girl

40:18.880 --> 40:20.848
even for the
blink of an eye.

40:20.880 --> 40:24.714
But it happened, and it's
always going to have happened.

40:24.750 --> 40:26.980
(Gulping)

40:27.020 --> 40:28.909
- Listen, just don't
move, all right?

40:28.960 --> 40:31.110
I've--I've been
through worse, believe me.

40:31.160 --> 40:32.855
All right?
We're gonna fix this.

40:32.890 --> 40:35.154
- Guess we have something
else in common now.

40:35.200 --> 40:36.929
Sally's gone.

40:39.030 --> 40:41.192
She's gone.

40:42.640 --> 40:44.460
- What?

40:44.510 --> 40:46.205
- Sally's...
- No, she's not.

40:46.240 --> 40:49.870
- No, she is. Sally's gone,
and Josh destroyed her.

40:51.910 --> 40:55.642
He ruined the one good--
the one good thing that you had.

40:55.680 --> 40:57.671
This is what he does.

40:57.720 --> 41:00.109
This is all Josh's fault.

41:01.960 --> 41:03.951
It's all Josh's fault.

41:07.090 --> 41:08.751
- Oh!

41:08.800 --> 41:10.655
(Stake clattering)

41:22.240 --> 41:23.708
(Whimpering)

41:25.250 --> 41:27.901
(Aidan sobbing)

41:30.620 --> 41:32.110
Oh God!

41:32.150 --> 41:33.686
- Guys.

41:38.090 --> 41:40.024
- By all means,
join him.

41:43.260 --> 41:45.820
(Aidan sobbing)

42:01.620 --> 42:03.748
- I lied for you.

42:03.780 --> 42:05.680
- Aidan.

42:05.720 --> 42:08.212
- And now my son is dead.

42:08.250 --> 42:10.150
And Sally!

42:10.190 --> 42:11.726
- Aidan!

42:13.990 --> 42:16.698
- It was the one thing

42:16.730 --> 42:19.028
that gave me any hope!

42:19.070 --> 42:20.822
- (Donna):
When I send you forward,

42:20.870 --> 42:23.840
you may bounce around in time
a little bit first.

42:23.870 --> 42:26.840
- It was the one thing
that gave me any hope!

42:26.870 --> 42:28.304
- Josh! Hey!

42:28.340 --> 42:31.310
- I know you're confused,
but I can explain this, pal.

42:31.340 --> 42:32.603
- This is on you.

42:32.650 --> 42:33.879
- No.

42:33.910 --> 42:35.719
Aidan, no.
Don't do this!

42:35.750 --> 42:37.969
Back up right now!
- I can explain this.

42:38.020 --> 42:39.715
- This is on you.
- STOP!

